    "-Parameter sensitivity: The choice of parameters significantly impacts the performance of MHO algorithms.",
    "It can be challenging to enhance these parameters, and it frequently calls for in-depth research or domain experience [61].",
    "-Dataset complexity: Transactions may be misclassified due to the algorithm's inability to efficiently explore the search space and come up with a suitable solution due to the dataset's complexity, which includes high dimensionality, class imbalance, and incomplete data [75].RQ5: What future directions are recommended for ML, DL, and MHO models in detecting CCF attacks?• ML Models -Integration with Real-time Fraud Detection: ML models can be better integrated with real-time FD systems to promptly respond to suspicious transactions without affecting accuracy.",
